page_0: "We finally reset all the traps in the temple as Vivianne requested. I tell ya, I've never felt so close to mutiny. I reckon she's lost it is what. What the hell does she think she'll find down in that damn temple. We got enough treasure already surely. Although, I'll admit to being sorely frustrated by those crystal barriers blocking some of the doorways. I can see some good treasure behind them, but nothing we try will shift the crystals. We've tried bashing at em, shooting them, even tried a mine and a fire arrow. Must be some magic keeping em sealed."
